decisionmakingagent

Class PotentialWord

  • java.lang.Object
    • decisionmakingagent.PotentialWord

  • public class PotentialWord
extends java.lang.Object
    The PotentialWord class acts solely as a wrapper for a number of Neurons that come as one potential combination of the Neurons in the PotentialChar objects that compose a word. The resulting array of Neurons is encapsulated to increase readability.
    Author:
    Nathan Van Dyken, Sulman Qureshi
